description:
NOTE: I've been told the only way to collect Blaze Rods post 1.9-pre1 is if you kill the Blaze yourself and that suffocation doesn't work. I have not confirmed this myself yet. This video demonstrates how to conquer a Blaze spawner.

This tutorial shows you one possible way of setting up an automatic Blaze Farm in the nether.
